java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeImplStateNames, IAeImplVisitor
public class AeRestoreImplStateVisitor
extends AeBaseRestoreVisitor

Visits a tree of BPEL implementation objects to restore the state from an instance of AeRestoreImplState.
